    <h2 id="open-calculations" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Open Calculations</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/004/002/661/original/cc7c2769-5af1-4a1b-845b-7c067308adad.png" srcset="" alt="Open Calculations" height="69" width="345">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_296b418b-0b8a-4375-b744-f637116a0cea" class="text-block-content">
    <p>To view and manage the mastery calculation method, click the <strong>Calculation</strong> tab.</p>
<p><strong>Note: </strong>If the Calculation tab does not display in the Outcomes page, account-level outcome mastery calculations have not been enabled by your institution.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
