      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_03f09110-bc70-43e9-b762-65dfc5887774" class="text-block-content">
    <p>To select the highest score from all assessment items, select the <strong>Highest Score</strong> option [1].</p>
<p>You can view an example of the Highest Score calculation in the <strong>Example</strong> section [2].</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

